metadata.name: Like Stars in the Sky
metadata.description:
Up in the Sky
I see tiny stars starting to appear
Pink, purple clouds in the Sky from there to here
Twinkling, shining dots, but they didn't seem very clear 
Street lights, city lights
The stars slowly fade and disappear
I wish I could see them 
Maybe just for few mins or forever

So I created my night sky with stars and planets in my room
A tiny spaceship and rocket, so I can fly to the moon
Quick round, around the rings of Saturn
Zeep Zamp Zoom
I see a pale blue dot, far away
And a couple of Saturn moons

The Sky is full of stars and they are moving very slow
Connecting stars and lines together, they start to glow
It's like those constellations that I saw in the school books
Shooting stars just flying past
Hey, Look!

Hey, do you see this?
This bright blue star in my room
So bright, like those circles in the Sky
Like that orange Sun and that yellow Moon

Can we get a bit closer?
Have a look at the Bright Star 
Will play Some nice music
And we can Stargaze just for few mins or forever
